{"word":"Incense","slug":"incense","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Incense</b> Formula for compounding<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=35'>Exo 30:35</a><br/> Uses of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=38'>Exo 30:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=16&verse=12'>Lev 16:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16&verse=17'>Num 16:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16&verse=40'>Num 16:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16&verse=46'>Num 16:46</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=33&verse=10'>Deu 33:10</a><br/> Compounded by Bezaleel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=37&verse=29'>Exo 37:29</a><br/> Compounded by priests<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=9&verse=30'>1Ch 9:30</a><br/> Offered:<br/> - Morning and evening<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=8'>Exo 30:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=13&verse=11'>2Ch 13:11</a> <br/> - On the golden altar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=7'>Exo 30:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=5'>Exo 40:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=40&verse=27'>Exo 40:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=2&verse=4'>2Ch 2:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=32&verse=12'>2Ch 32:12</a> <br/> - In making atonement<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=16&verse=13'>Lev 16:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16&verse=47'>Num 16:47</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=10'>Luk 1:10</a> <br/> Unlawfully offered by:<br/> - Nadab and Abihu<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=10&verse=2'>Lev 10:2</a> <br/> - Korah, Dathan, and Abiram<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=16&verse=35'>Num 16:35</a> <br/> - Uzziah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=21'>2Ch 26:21</a> <br/> Offered in idolatrous worship<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=12&verse=33'>1Ki 12:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=41&verse=5'>Jer 41:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=8&verse=11'>Eze 8:11</a><br/> Presented by the wise men to Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=2&verse=11'>Mat 2:11</a><br/><a href='S:Altar, Of Incense'>Altar, Of Incense</a><br/> Figurative:<br/> - Of prayer<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=141&verse=2'>Psa 141:2</a> <br/> - Of praise<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=1&verse=11'>Mal 1:11</a> <br/> - Of an acceptable sacrifice<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=5&verse=2'>Eph 5:2</a> <br/> Symbolic of the prayers of saints<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=5&verse=8'>Rev 5:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=8&verse=4'>Rev 8:4</a>"}]}